main event: A sighting of a very fast object was reported in Sequim, Washington on 2 Sep 55.
interesting points: The object was described as the size of a large c/c., The object emitted a sound that was heard during the sighting., The observation lasted for approximately 2 minutes., Both civilian and military sources contributed to the report., The sighting occurred during daylight hours.
sighted object: unknown object described as very fast
witness description: the sighting was reported by a civilian
